data.title: Dean's List Recipients
data.meta_description: The following Wake Forest University students have been named to the university’s Dean’s List.
data.text:
University Registrar Announcement:

Student Action Required: Fall 2024 Onboarding Tasks

Students, please check your Workday My Tasks inbox for onboarding tasks for the fall 2024 semester. Until you complete these tasks, you will not have access to registration activities including adding, dropping and swapping courses. You must also click Submit on every task or your onboarding will remain incomplete. If your inbox does not list any tasks, you have already completed your onboarding. Workday Student helpline: 336.758.5600

The following Wake Forest University students have been named to the university’s Dean’s List. Full-time, degree-seeking students in the College and the School of Business who achieve a 3.4 or better for a full-time course load in the semester and who have earned no grade below C during the semester were named to the list.

Spring 2024
